snippet.title: Sea of Thieves Gameplay Reveal - Xbox E3 2016
snippet.description:
SEA OF THIEVES GAMEPLAY REVEAL E3 TRAILER.  XBOX ONE & WINDOWS 10 EXCLUSIVE | Be the first to watch fans play Sea of Thieves for the first time.  Learn more on Xbox.com.

Xbox Live Gold required to play (sold separately).
